<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_C_062">Enter only numbers and - in the contact information.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_063">You can add and modify the category / classification / facility in the Reservation menu.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_064">You can add / modify / delete the the category in the Reservation menu.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_065">You can add / modify the category by directly entering the category name / explanation.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_066">You can add / modify / delete the classification of the category in the Reservation menu.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_067">You can designate the upper category of the classifiacation. And you can add/modify the classification by directly entering the classification name / explanation.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_068">You can add / modify / delete the facility in the Reservation menu..</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_069">After designating the upper category and setting the sub-classification of the category and you can modify / add the facility.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_070">Facility Name / Explanation : Enter the facility name / explanation directly.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_071">Reservation way : You can set the reservation way of the facility by selecting between "Open reservation" and "After Admin's Apr".</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_072">Usable time : You can set the usable time of the facility.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_073">Admin Notification : You can select the notification method to be sent to the facility administrator.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_074">Facility Status: You can set whether to use the facility.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_075">Location / Uable Condition / Approval Process : Enter the location and condition of the facility directly.</entry>
<entry key="PC.EAU.RE_H_076">Facility Administrator: If you click the [Organization Chart] button, you can designate and delete an administrator through the “Facility Administrator” pop-up window.</entry>
